            Or simply forward this email to help spread the word
          </mj-text>
        </mj-column>
      </mj-section>
      
      <!-- Thank You Section -->
      <mj-section background-color="#1a2332" padding="25px 20px">
        <mj-column>
          <mj-text align="center" color="#ffffff">
            <strong>Thank you for being part of this effort.</strong><br/>
            Together we're protecting our neighbourhood streets.
